name: PUPKIN
description:
Binomial Name : Canis Cucurbita 
Height : 60 cm
Length : 65 cm
Conservation Status : Endangered (Seasonal Bizarre Pet for Halloween 2021)
Diet : Pumpkin Pie, Sweets, and Teeth with cavities.

Someone knocked my shop's door, and gave me some pumpkin seeds. She said I just need to throw the seeds under the moonlight. I saw them running in my backyards in the morning.
